Package semsim.model.computational.datastructures

Class DataStructure

java.lang.Object
semsim.SemSimObject
semsim.model.SemSimComponent
semsim.model.computational.ComputationalModelComponent
semsim.model.computational.datastructures.DataStructure
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, Annotatable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Decimal, MMLchoice, SemSimInteger
public abstract class DataStructure
extends ComputationalModelComponent
implements Annotatable, java.lang.Cloneable
This class represents a symbolic element in a simulation model that is assigned some computational value during simulation.
